{
  "key": 54005,
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "Cafe_Text_CustomersWantToBattle",
      "en_US": [
        "Howdy, traveler!\r",
        "Some of our customers are rowdy\n",
        "types that want to battle.\r",
        "Do what you will with them.\n",
        "I don’t mind."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Cafe_Text_MoomooMilk500ABottle",
      "en_US": [
        "How are ya doing?\n",
        "Whatcha having?\r",
        "Course, all we ever have is\n",
        "Moomoo Milk.\r",
        "Moomoo Milk, $500 a bottle.\r",
        "Would you like to add some to your\n",
        "traveling supplies?"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Cafe_Text_HeresYourMoomooMilk",
      "en_US": [
        "Here’s your Moomoo Milk.\n",
        "Enjoy.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Cafe_Text_YourBagsFull",
      "en_US": [
        "Oh!\n",
        "Your Bag’s full, sweetie."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Cafe_Text_YouDontHaveTheMoney",
      "en_US": [
        "Oh!\n",
        "You don’t have the money, sweetie."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Cafe_Text_AllRightThen",
      "en_US": [
        "All right, then.\r",
        "I should tell you, it’s not that we\n",
        "can only get Moomoo Milk. No.\r",
        "We choose to serve only Moomoo Milk.\n",
        "We’re very particular about it."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Cafe_Text_GetMoomooMilkByDozen",
      "en_US": [
        "Get your Moomoo Milk by the dozen.\n",
        "That’s of course twelve to a dozen.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Cafe_Text_1Bottle",
      "en_US": "1 BOTTLE"
    },
    {
      "id": "Cafe_Text_1Dozen",
      "en_US": "1 DOZEN"
    },
    {
      "id": "Cafe_Text_NoThanks",
      "en_US": "NO THANKS"
    },
    {
      "id": "Cafe_Text_SeenPsyduckHuddledOutside",
      "en_US": [
        "Youngster, you’ve seen the\n",
        "PSYDUCK huddled outside?\r",
        "PSYDUCK are Pokémon that suffer from\n",
        "chronic headaches...\r",
        "I’m afraid we’ll have to wait for them\n",
        "to get better."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "Cafe_Text_RelievedPsyduckOfHeadaches",
      "en_US": [
        "Well, well! So I hear you’ve relieved\n",
        "the PSYDUCK of their headaches.\r",
        "The person who gave you the\n",
        "SecretPotion must be quite the Trainer!"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
